      • inputTextField

        javax.swing.JTextField[] inputTextField
        inputTextField is a JTextField to get user input, it is done as an array to keep the code consise. it is assumed that the values for all the arrays go in the following order: r - hare birth rate a - puma predation rate b - puma birth rate m - puma death rate k - hare diffusion rate l - puma diffusion rate dt - time step
